{{Unreferenced|date=April 2016}} {{Infobox company | name = RTV Noord | logo = RTV Noord.png | logo_caption = | image = | image_caption = | trading_name = | native_name = | native_name_lang = <!-- Use ISO 639-1 code, e.g. "fr" for French. For multiple names in different languages, use {{lang|[code]|[name]}} instead. --> | romanized_name = | former_name = | former type = | type = | traded_as = | industry = [[Mass media]] | genre = <!-- Only used with media and publishing companies --> | fate = | predecessor = [[Radio Noord]] | successors = <!-- or: | successor = --> | foundation = <!-- City, Country ({{start date|YYYY|MM|DD}}) --> | founders = <!-- or: | founders = --> | defunct = <!-- {{end date|YYYY|MM|DD}} --> | location_city = [[Groningen]] | location_country = [[Netherlands]] | locations = <!-- Number of locations --> | area_served = [[Groningen (province)|Groningen]] | key_people = | products = | brands = | production = | services = | revenue = | operating_income = | net_income = | aum = <!-- Only for financial-service companies --> | assets = | equity = | owners = <!-- or: | owner = --> | num_employees = | parent = | divisions = | subsid = | homepage = {{URL|www.rtvnoord.nl}} | footnotes = | intl = <!-- Use "true" or "yes", otherwise omit --> | bodystyle = }}
'''RTV Noord''' is a regional radio and television [[Public broadcasting|public broadcaster]] in [[Groningen (province)|Groningen]], [[Netherlands]]. {{As of|2013}} its radio programs are broadcast on [[Frequency modulation|FM]] 97.5 [[MHz]]. It broadcasts TV and radio programming 24 hours per day, seven days a week. Some content is broadcast in the [[Gronings dialect]] of [[Dutch language|Dutch]]. A popular part of the broadcaster's website is "Groningen in Beeld" ("Groningen in pictures"), which features pictures of Groningen Province uploaded by listeners. ==See also== * [[Netherlands Public Broadcasting]] ==References== {{reflist}} ==External links== * {{official|http://www.rtvnoord.nl}} * [http://www.rtvnoord.nl/groningeninbeeld/index1.asp Groningen in Beeld]
