{{Unreferenced|date=December 2009}}
{{italic title}}
[[Image:Arrogant Worms Three Worms and an Orchestra.jpg|thumb|''Three Worms and an Orchestra'' DVD cover.]]
'''''Three Worms and an Orchestra''''' is a [[DVD]] of a performance of the [[Canada|Canadian]] comedy music group [[The Arrogant Worms]] with the [[Edmonton Symphony Orchestra]]. It includes their most popular songs performed live, as well as two [[music video]]s.

The original, and heavily edited, version of this performance aired on [[Bravo! Canada]]. The Arrogant Worms also released a related CD, ''[[Semi-Conducted]]'', with most of the tracks on it.

{{The Arrogant Worms}}

